<P>
MAN, 36, IS SHOT AND KILLED AT MOTEL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A 36-year-old man was shot and killed early Sunday morning at the Comfort Inn 
on Sepulveda Boulevard after arguing with his killer, police said. 
</P>
<P>
 Humberto Castrejon died at the scene about 3:30 a.m. after being shot in the 
chest, said Police Sgt. Michael Sonntag. 
