<HEADLINE>
<P>
MOURNING A PET LOST TO COYOTES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 * My adorable poodle "Cream Puff" was taken out of my yard by a coyote in 
February, 1993.My yard is fenced, but the coyote still got in. 
</P>
<P>
 I put signs out after the incident to warn others with small animals and 
children. 
</P>
<P>
 The city animal-control commissioners should order the trapping of coyotes 
again. My dog was like my child and best friend, and I have been heartsick all 
year. 
</P>
<P>
 MAXINE TOBEY 
</P>
<P>
 Encino 
</P>
