<HEADLINE>
<P>
CALENDAR GOES TO THE OSCARS; AND LAST YEAR'S WINNERS WERE . . . 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 As Hollywood gears up for its big night, does anyone remember who won just a 
year ago? A reminder: 
</P>
<P>
 Picture: "Unforgiven" Director: Clint Eastwood, "Unforgiven" Actor: Al Pacino, 
"Scent of a Woman" Actress: Emma Thompson, "Howards End" Supporting Actor: Gene 
Hackman, "Unforgiven" Supporting Actress: Marisa Tomei, "My Cousin Vinny" 
Original Screenplay: Neil Jordan, "The Crying Game" Adapted Screenplay: Ruth 
Prawer Jhabvala, "Howards End" 
