</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA032194-0202 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 025007 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
March 21, 1994, Monday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Part D; Page 6; Column 1; Financial Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
37 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY NEWSMAKERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Kevin Kearns has joined Foresight, a Newport Beach property maintenance 
company, as senior accounts manager. He was previously vice president and real 
estate development associate for CMS Development Co. in Costa Mesa. 
</P>
