</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 GALLERY -- An art gallery in Santa Monica owned by Mark Moore is called the 
Mark Moore Gallery. It was misidentified in Thursday's Calendar. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Correction 
</P>
</TYPE>
